<div class="note-source" id="TSJN-01-01-0213-sn">
<p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ recipient's copy ]">RC</abbr> (<span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Library of Congress ]">DLC</span>). <a id="TSJN-01-01-0213-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to Dead lift in text" href="#TSJN-01-01-0213-ks-0001">Dead lift</a>: A position or juncture in which one can do no more, an extremity (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;A New English Dictionary on Historical Principles&lt;/i&gt;, Oxford, 18881933 ]">OED</span>).</p></div>
